39:08.387 --> 39:11.098
Thank God Andre didn't leave
when I told him to.

39:13.559 --> 39:15.186
Thank God you didn't catch up

39:15.269 --> 39:18.773
to that hillbilly in the woods.
He might've killed you, Archie.

39:18.856 --> 39:20.524
And that would've been--

39:34.789 --> 39:38.000
<i>Archie didn't say any more</i>
<i>about what happened that terrible night.</i>

39:38.918 --> 39:40.961
<i>At least not to us.</i>

39:44.757 --> 39:47.176
Veronica told me
what happened at the cabin.

39:47.676 --> 39:50.179
And then Andre told me the rest.

39:50.262 --> 39:53.391
You did the right thing telling those boys
to take what they wanted and get out.

39:53.474 --> 39:54.850
It was a smart choice.

39:56.685 --> 39:58.187
It was the only choice.

40:00.398 --> 40:03.275
-Thank you for saying that, Mr. Lodge.
-Yeah.

40:08.280 --> 40:12.743
What happened between Andre
and that miscreant...

40:14.537 --> 40:15.871
Did that bother you?

40:17.581 --> 40:19.959
What Andre did?

40:23.712 --> 40:25.840
The night we stopped the Black Hood...

40:27.925 --> 40:30.428
there's only one thing that I regret.

40:31.595 --> 40:32.471
I had him.

40:33.431 --> 40:35.891
The man who tried to kill my dad,
I had him.

40:37.810 --> 40:39.019
And I hesitated.

40:40.980 --> 40:43.566
He might've gotten away
if it wasn't for Sheriff Keller.

40:44.150 --> 40:47.361
When it comes to protecting yourself
or your loved ones...

40:48.863 --> 40:51.031
you never, ever, hesitate.

41:05.713 --> 41:08.549
You can stop worrying now. I'm home.

41:10.050 --> 41:12.845
As we were driving back from The Shining,
I was thinking...

41:13.262 --> 41:15.806
there's more than one kind
of home invasion.

41:15.890 --> 41:17.892
It's not always fast and violent.

41:17.975 --> 41:20.936
Sometimes we open the door,
and we let the intruder in ourselves.

41:22.313 --> 41:23.481
What do you mean?

41:25.274 --> 41:28.319
Before we left,
I got a really weird vibe from Chic.

41:30.488 --> 41:31.780
Just be careful, okay?

41:38.704 --> 41:40.164
-Bye.
-Bye.

41:45.461 --> 41:47.755
<i>And so this chapter comes full circle,</i>

41:48.380 --> 41:49.715
<i>ending where it began,</i>

41:50.257 --> 41:54.553
<i>with a girl in a house</i>
<i>that was far from sweet.</i>
